column5: Seems like i lost my camera out on the ice either at the end of salvation army rd/Franklin beach.  Or out on the ice northwest of georgina or straight north past all the huts at jacksons point........ Pretty expensive trip for only a few hours each day sat and sunday!  Its in a black case keep your eyes open for me fellas!
tough break , hope if someone finds it they are an OFNr! TB
If I find it, I'll sell it to ya for a good price!!!
Was thinking the same thing!!! Then I thought no....Tony's camera is better then mine...keep his and sell him mine
